## Python Programs Practiced

### Log Analyzer
```python
with open("security.log", "r") as file:
    count = 0

    for line in file:
        if "error" in line.lower():
            count += 1

print("Errors Found:", count)
```

### IP Address Extractor
```python
import re

text = "User connected from 192.168.1.10"

ips = re.findall(r"\d+\.\d+\.\d+\.\d+", text)

print(ips)
```

### Port List Generator
```python
ports = {
    22: "SSH",
    53: "DNS",
    80: "HTTP",
    443: "HTTPS"
}

for port, service in ports.items():
    print(port, service)
```

